33#include "gmp.h"
34#include "gmp-impl.h"
35
36void
37mpn_cnd_swap (mp_limb_t cnd, volatile mp_limb_t *ap, volatile mp_limb_t *bp,
38 mp_size_t n)
39{
40 volatile mp_limb_t mask = - (mp_limb_t) (cnd != 0);
41 mp_size_t i;
42 for (i = 0; i < n; i++)
43 {
44 mp_limb_t a, b, t;
45 a = ap[i];
46 b = bp[i];
47 t = (a ^ b) & mask;
48 ap[i] = a ^ t;
49 bp[i] = b ^ t;
50 }
51}
